# AION – AI Chat Module (Decision Engine)

AION is a high-performance, multitenant AI Decision Engine built with **Python**, **FastAPI**, and **LangGraph**. It acts as the "brain" for Instagram commerce, processing DMs and comments to manage inventory inquiries, order flows, and customer support in both English and Roman Urdu.

## 🚀 Overview
AION receives structured chat events and business context, then decides the next best action—whether to reply to the customer, trigger a backend order draft, or escalate to a human agent. It is strictly a **decision engine** and does not handle Meta APIs or token storage directly.

## 🏗️ Architecture
The system uses a **Stateless Multi-Agent State Machine** architecture:
- **FastAPI**: Handles the REST interface and multi-tenancy isolation.
- **LangGraph**: Orchestrates the conversation flow and state transitions.
- **Google Gemini 1.5**: Powers the reasoning, classification, and multilingual responses.
- **Pydantic v2**: Ensures strict JSON schema validation for all inputs and outputs.

## 📂 Project Structure
```text
aion-chatbot-service/
├── app/
│   ├── core/
│   │   ├── config.py      # Environment & Gemini settings
│   │   └── prompts.py     # System instructions (Intents & Roman Urdu)
│   ├── schemas/
│   │   └── chat.py        # Pydantic Models (Section 2 & 3 Validation)
│   ├── services/
│   │   ├── nodes.py       # Logic: Classifier, Commerce, & Translator
│   │   ├── state.py       # TypedDict for LangGraph State
│   │   └── graph.py       # Workflow & Edge logic
│   ├── routes/
│   │   └── chat_routes.py # FastAPI POST /process-chat
│   └── main.py            # FastAPI Entry Point
├── .env                   # API Keys (GOOGLE_API_KEY)
└── requirements.txt       # Dependencies